# Allowed on-prem (or other) source IPs/CIDRs for inbound HEC (8088) and S2S (9997).
# Copy to nsg-allowed-sources.conf and edit (or set NSG_ALLOWED_SOURCES_FILE in .env).
#
# One address or prefix per line. Lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# Examples:
# 203.0.113.50              # single corporate egress IP
# 10.20.0.0/16              # on-prem network via VPN
# 192.168.1.0/24

203.0.113.50
10.20.0.0/16
